## Ожидаемый урон за раунд (DPR)

```
DPR = P(hit) × P(kill|hit) × Shots
```

| Оружие | Combat | DPR vs T4 |
|--------|--------|-----------|
| Military Rifle | +1 | 0.50 × 0.50 × 1 = 0.25 |
| Auto Rifle | +1 | 0.50 × 0.50 × 2 = 0.50 |
| Shotgun | +1 | 0.50 × 0.67 × 2 = 0.67 |
| Plasma Rifle | +1 | 0.50 × 0.67 × 2 = 0.67 |

